"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"> The speech in the silence:\\n>\\n> The words against the son of night:\\n>\\n> The voice of Thoth before the universe in the presence of the eternal gods:\\n>\\n> The formulas of knowledge:\\n>\\n> The wisdom of breath:\\n>\\n> The radix of vibration:\\n>\\n> The shaking of the invisible:\\n>\\n> The rolling asunder of the darkness:\\n>\\n> The becoming visible of matter:\\n>\\n> The piercing of the coils of the stooping dragon:\\n>\\n> The breaking forth of the light:\\n>\\n> All these are in the knowledge of Tho-oth.\\n\\n以上开场引用自金色黎明(Hermetic Order of the Golden Dawn)在Z1书中记录的通用绪论(general exordium)，也作为本人使用Mirror这个Web3创作平台的一个新的起点。这个站点会专注于西方神秘学方面的写作，尤其是以克劳利(Aleister Crowley)为代表的Thelema这个神秘学体系。从神秘学角度来看，这些文字作品只是作者内在心境的外在显化，只反映了在那个时刻的initiation（启蒙）等级，今后伴随着新的领悟，可能会也可能不会赞同之前作品中的部分观点。\\n\\n下一步作者会佛系搬运一些自己之前在知乎上的文章，让它们来到去中心化的网络，重获免于被审查删稿的自由～\\n\\n### English version:\\n\\nThe quote above is the general exordium from the Z1 book of the Hermetic Order of the Golden Dawn, which also initiates my new endeavor into this Web3 world, with Mirror being the first. This personal site will be dedicated to discussions of western esotericism, especially Aleister Crowley’s lineage known as Thelema, as well as other general teachings from the Hermetic Order of the Golden Dawn.\\n\\nFrom the esoteric point of view, all my writings are just a reflection of my current inner world and understanding, and subjected to change based on new light from my future initiations. In this way the author may not necessarily agree with everything in his earlier works.\\n\\nThis site will be mostly written in Chinese, as an exodus from the dire censorship in China right now. Web3 is the only solution to obtain real freedom and ownership of our digital properties.\",\"timestamp\":1637547583,\"title\":\"An introduction to western esotericism（一个关于西方神秘学的站点）\"},\"digest\":\"zc9rSOVlgHKW1QkqH7kuKWZn1WumT3qbLkncwtFqoSQ\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x29Fc29a1D4E9D8391e0F1cd6fF7BEF16D83aB36c\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"gxZn8tKtkzLLR5RTNmu1JR9XaiRPGJOL5f-B7GWng7g\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"5GDd5UWqZsigYfTv5tWYGQxVyyYjrs-JzK_yGmgFynI\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"YhiMu5TqfAXyr0kjk7UD4U_Xzpvde2abHdozgWn9yHqEN1ibaks-_mo_TGv-bp2zihgMqVkMnqKW-2zRGak2pA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x8e1aa9f89760f8353e904f09d587ff9987c954226769c5d4942cb89abbdb095300365bb8bd80e0df538303f84b4c577c40f84dace020152889260bef4ce7feb81b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"gxZn8tKtkzLLR5RTNmu1JR9XaiRPGJOL5f-B7GWng7g\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"5GDd5UWqZsigYfTv5tWYGQxVyyYjrs-JzK_yGmgFynI\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"CxIugtoOiRjWNbfCW2Ts_u5vcdokHGZDGof04-4c7Ok\"}"